{"word":"πῶς","slug":"πῶς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πῶς</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> the element <el>πο-</el>in <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πόθεν\">πόθεν</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> introducing a query concerning manner, way, or reason in respect to a matter <b>how? in what manner/way? <p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> direct<b><p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>α.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on quest for information <b>how? <a href='B:490 1:34'>Lk 1:34</a>; <a href='B:490 10:26'>10:26</a>; <a href='B:500 3:9'>J 3:9</a>; <a href='B:500 9:10'>9:10</a>, <a href='B:500 9:19'>19</a>, <a href='B:500 9:26'>26</a>; <a href='B:520 4:10'>Ro 4:10</a>; <a href='B:530 15:35'>1 Cor 15:35</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>β.</pp></b> in a variety of formulations, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ esp.\">esp.</a> in argumentative contexts: in expression of wonder or surprise <b>how is it then? how can it be that? <a href='B:470 16:11'>Mt 16:11</a>; <a href='B:470 22:43'>22:43</a>, <a href='B:470 22:45'>45</a>; <a href='B:480 9:12'>Mk 9:12</a>; <a href='B:490 11:18'>Lk 11:18</a>; <a href='B:490 20:41'>20:41</a>, <a href='B:490 20:44'>44</a>; <a href='B:500 3:4'>J 3:4</a>; <a href='B:500 4:9'>4:9</a>; <a href='B:500 12:34'>12:34</a>; <a href='B:510 2:8'>Ac 2:8</a>; <a href='B:550 4:9'>Gal 4:9</a>;</b> in criticism <b>how? by what right? <a href='B:470 7:4'>Mt 7:4</a>; <a href='B:470 22:12'>22:12</a>; <a href='B:490 6:42'>Lk 6:42</a>; <a href='B:500 6:42'>J 6:42</a>; <a href='B:530 15:12'>1 Cor 15:12</a>; <a href='B:550 2:14'>Gal 2:14</a>;</b> in request for clarification <b>how? in what sense? <a href='B:490 20:41'>Lk 20:41</a>; <a href='B:500 8:33'>J 8:33</a>; <a href='B:500 12:34'>12:34</a>;</b> in rhetorical statement inviting negation <b>how? in what way? <a href='B:470 12:26'>Mt 12:26</a>, <a href='B:470 12:29'>29</a>, <a href='B:470 12:34'>34</a>; <a href=